

= "The full-featured Wiki for all things Gun Printing"

URL = http://defensedistributed.com/wiki/index.php?title=Main_Page


=Description=

"As Defense Distributed finishes tooling up for the production of Wiki Weapons, we have begun building a collaborative community for the sharing of knowledge related to printable firearms and their manufacture.

As word of the WikiWep project has grown, the most consistent contributions we've received have been from engineers, firearm enthusiasts and hobbyists offering their takes and critiques on the problems posed by our goal: a fully-functioning firearm printed from thermoset.
Let's build a hub here. A redoubt for fugitive information, a strong resource for the adept, and a helpful bazaar for the uninitiated."

